com.digitalpersona.uareu

Interface Fmd.Fmv

  • Enclosing interface:
    Fmd

    public static interface Fmd.Fmv
    Class represents Fingerprint Minutiae Data (FMD).

    Class reflects ANSI INSITS 378-2004 and ISO IEC 19794-2-2005 formats.

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      byte[] getData()
      Returns complete binary data of a view, including view header and extended data block
      byte[] getExtBlockData()
      Returns extended data block
      int getFingerPosition()
      Returns finger position, 0 - 10, from Table 1 in "ANSI INSITS 378-2004"
      int getImpressionType()
      Returns impression type, from Table 2 in "ANSI INSITS 378-2004"
      int getMinutiaCnt()
      Returns number of minutiae
      int getQuality()
      Returns quality, 1 - 100
      int getViewNumber()
      Returns view number, 0 - 15
